  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: User types one amount, adds transaction to Unsigned, opens Unsigned list and sees other amount both in the list and in the transaction details:\r\n1. `123456789012345678901` was typed but sum is shown as `1234567890123456780000` in Unsigned list and in transaction details. Pay attention to the end of the sum\r\n2. `1234567890,123456789012345678` was typed but sum is shown as `1234567890,12345679` in Unsigned list and in transaction details. If use Sign then Send Transaction screen is opened with amount shown as `1234567890,12345679` that is really wrong. If I scheduled transaction with amount X I would like to send that exact X amount.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n1. exact amount typed by a user is shown on the Transaction details screen\r\n2. exact amount typed by a user is shown on Send transaction screen is user taped on Sign under the unsigned transaction\r\n3. some truncated amount (at the end of the sum) is shown on Unsigned list for the transaction it it does not fit the line. e.g. for `123456789012345678901 ETH` it can be `12345678901234567... ETH`\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nhttps://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803590-status/builds/6869567/sessions/2/?accessToken=08ZnVLBN-Vt3s7KMaT0zA9v/-8c\r\n1. `123456789012345678901` was typed but sum is shown as `1234567890123456780000` in Unsigned list and in transaction details. Pay attention to the end of the sum\r\n2. `1234567890,123456789012345678` was typed but sum is shown as `1234567890,12345679` in Unsigned list and in transaction details. If use Sign then Send Transaction screen is opened with amount shown as `1234567890,12345679`\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Open Wallet \r\n- Send `123456789012345678901` to Jarrad (use Sign Later to add transaction ti Unsigned)\r\n- Open Transactions -> Unsigned and check sum shown in the list and transaction details screen for sum\r\n- Tap on Sign to get Send Transaction screen and check Amount field - should contain exact amount typed by a user\r\n- return to Wallet \r\n- Send `1234567890,123456789012345678` to Jarrad (use Sign Later to add transaction ti Unsigned)\r\n- Open Transactions -> Unsigned and check sum shown in the list and transaction details screen for sum\r\n- Tap on Sign to get Send Transaction screen and check Amount field - should contain exact amount typed by a user\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: develop  0.9.11d242 \r\n* Operating System: \r\nReal device iPhone 6s, iOs 10.3.3\r\n\r\n",
